msgstr "在 :guilabel:`允许` 字段中选择其他财务状况，以便在销售过程中可供选择。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/pricing.rst:234
msgid ""
"Depending on the installed :doc:`fiscal localization package </applications/"
