msgstr ":doc:`../../payment_methods`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:3
msgid "Glory"
msgstr "Glory"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Glory** :doc:`cash machines <../cash_machines>` enable the automation of "
"cash transactions."
msgstr "**Glory** :doc:`收银机 <../cash_machines>` 可实现现金交易自动化。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:8
msgid "Odoo supports the Glory CI-5, CI-10, and CI-10X models."
msgstr "Odoo 支持 Glory CI-5、CI-10 和 CI-10X 型号。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Glory machine must run firmware version ISP-K05H/B v18.40 or later. Any "
"version starting with ISP-K35 is **not supported**."
msgstr ""
"Glory 设备必须运行 ISP-K05H/B v18.40 或更高版本固件。以 ISP-K35 开头的任何版"
"本均**不支持**。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:12
msgid ""
"The integration with the Glory cash machine only supports basic functions, "
"such as cash transactions and cash count checks."
msgstr "与 Glory 收银机的集成仅支持基础功能，如现金交易与现金盘点。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:23
msgid "Cash machine settings"
msgstr "收银机设置"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:25
msgid ""
"Power on the cash machine, which briefly displays its IP address at the "
"bottom of the screen. Note it down for later."
msgstr "开机后，屏幕底部会短暂显示 IP 地址，请记下备用。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:29
msgid ""
"The IP address should be formatted as `###.###.#.##` (e.g., `192.168.0.25`)."
msgstr "IP 地址格式应为 ###.###.#.##（例如 192.168.0.25）。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:31
msgid ""
"Navigate to the cash machine's homepage by entering its IP address as the "
"URL in `HTTPS` (e.g., `https://192.168.0.25`), and log in with your Glory "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"在浏览器中以 HTTPS 协议输入该 IP 地址（如 `https://192.168.0.25`），访问收银"
"机主页，并使用 Glory 账号登录。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:33
msgid ""
"As long as the certificate is not imported, a warning page appears when "
"trying to access the machine's homepage. Bypass it by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Advanced` and then :guilabel:`Proceed to [IP address] "
"(unsafe)`."
msgstr ""
"若未导入证书，访问时会出现安全警告页面。点击 :guilabel:`高级` ，:guilabel:`继"
"续访问 [IP地址]（不安全）` 即可跳过。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:36
msgid ""
"From the Glory homepage, go to :guilabel:`Host Configuration` and ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Network` setting is set to :guilabel:`MANUAL`, meaning the IP "
"address is static."
msgstr ""
"从 Glory 首页，转到 :guilabel:`主机配置`，并确保 :guilabel:`网络` 设置为 "
":guilabel:`手动`，即使用静态 IP。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:38
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :guilabel:`SSL Configuration` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` section."
msgstr ""
"然后，导航至 :guilabel:`SSL 配置`，并向下滚动至 :guilabel:`HTTPS 服务器设置` "
"部分。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:41
msgid ""
"In parallel, open the terminal and verify that *OpenSSL* is installed. Type "
"`openssl` and press enter. If installed, this command displays a `help` menu "
"listing all available OpenSSL commands. If nothing happens, `install it "
"<https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."
msgstr ""
"同时，打开终端并确认是否已安装 *OpenSSL*。输入 `openssl` 并按回车键。如果已安"
"装，该命令会显示一个 `help` 菜单，列出所有可用的 OpenSSL 命令。如果没有反应，"
"请 `安装它 <https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:44
msgid ""
"Then, paste the following command and press `Enter` to generate and download "
"the certificate and private key. Ensure that you replace the demo IP address "
"with the cash machine’s actual IP address."
msgstr ""
"然后，粘贴以下命令并按下 `Enter` 键，以生成并下载证书和私钥。请务必将演示 IP "
"地址替换为 ATM 的实际 IP 地址。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:53
msgid ""
"The self-signed SSL certificate and key pair must use the same static IP "
"address as the cash machine."
msgstr "自签名 SSL 证书和密钥对必须使用与 ATM 机相同的静态 IP 地址。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once the files are generated, from the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` "
"section, upload `cert.pem` as the :guilabel:`Certificate` and `key.pem` as "
"the :guilabel:`Private Key`."
msgstr ""
"文件生成后，请在 :guilabel:`HTTPS 服务器设置` 部分，将 `cert.pem` 上传为 "
":guilabel:`证书`，并将 `key.pem` 上传为 :guilabel:`私钥`。"

