"，在\\ :guilabel:`产品与 POS 类别`\\ 部分的\\ :guilabel:`限制类别`\\ 字段中选"
"择相关类别。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:51
msgid "Product combos"
msgstr "产品组合"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:53
msgid ""
"A product combo is a bundle of multiple products sold together as a unit. "
"Each product combo consists of multiple categories, known as :ref:`combo "
"choices <pos/products/combo-choices>`, and each combo choice contains "
"several items. When purchasing a product combo, customers can select one or "
"more items from each combo choice."
msgstr ""
"产品套餐是作为一个单元一起销售的多个产品的组合。每个产品套餐由多个类别组成，"
"称为\\ :ref:`套餐选项 <pos/products/combo-choices>`，每个套餐选项包含多个项目"
"。购买产品套餐时，客户可以从每个套餐选项中选择一个或多个项目。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:59
msgid ""
"A burger menu is offered as a product combo including three combo choices: "
"one burger, one drink, and one portion of fries. For each combo choice, "
"customers select one item from the available options (e.g., cheeseburger or "
"chicken burger; soda or water; regular or large fries)."
msgstr ""
"汉堡套餐作为产品套餐提供，包括三个套餐选项：一个汉堡、一杯饮料和一份薯条。对"
"于每个套餐选项，客户从可用选项中选择一个项目（例如：芝士汉堡或鸡肉汉堡；苏打"
"水或水；普通薯条或大份薯条）。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:64
msgid ""
"`Product combos (video tutorial) <https://youtu.be/H8e2CakLhaQ?"
"si=yjPbvYkj00K7OP3q>`_"
msgstr "`产品套餐（视频教程）<https://youtu.be/H8e2CakLhaQ?si=yjPbvYkj00K7OP3q>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:69
