msgstr "选择\\ :doc:`付款方式 <payment_methods>`\\ ，然后根据需要输入金额。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:127
msgid ""
"Once payment is successful, the :doc:`receipt <use/receipts>` can be printed "
