msgstr "付款成功后，可以打印\\ :doc:`收据 <use/receipts>`\\ 或发送给客户。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:130
msgid ""
"To move on to the next order, click :guilabel:`New Order` on the receipt "
