#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:161
msgid ""
"To edit the customer's details, click the customer's name on the numpad, "
"click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon next to the "
"relevant customer, then select :guilabel:`Edit Details`."
msgstr ""
"要编辑客户详细信息，点击数字键盘上的客户名称，点击相关客户旁边的\\ :icon:`fa-"
"bars`\\ （:guilabel:`汉堡菜单`）图标，然后选择\\ :guilabel:`编辑详情`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:166
msgid ""
"Creating a new customer in the POS register or on the payment screen "
