#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:116
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button. On the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, there is a new "
"field: :guilabel:`Already invoiced` and :guilabel:`Amount to invoice`."
msgstr ""
"接下来，点击\\ :guilabel:`创建发票`\\ 按钮。在出现的\\ :guilabel:`创建发票`\\"
" 弹出窗口中，有一个新字段：:guilabel:`已开票`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`待开票金额`\\"
" 。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The deduct down payment option on the Create invoice(s) pop up in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售中创建发票弹出窗口上的扣除预付款选项。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:123
msgid ""
"If the remaining amount is ready to be paid, select the :guilabel:`Regular "
"Invoice` option. Odoo will create an invoice for the exact amount needed to "
"complete the total payment, as indicated in the :guilabel:`Amount to "
