#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:0
msgid "Example of a product variant type import spreadsheet."
msgstr "产品变体类型导入电子表格示例。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:247
msgid "Importing products and product variants from files"
msgstr "从文件导入产品和产品变体"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:249
msgid ""
"Files with product information can be imported from both the Product menu "
"and the Product Variants menu. By default, Odoo splits large files into "
"batches of 2,000 rows. For variant imports, all variants of the same "
"template must be imported in the same batch. To ensure that no products are "
"missed, set the import batch size to a greater amount than the number of "
"products to import."
msgstr ""
"可以从产品菜单和产品变体菜单导入包含产品信息的文件。默认情况下，Odoo 会将大型"
"文件拆分为每批 2,000 行。对于变体导入，同一模板的所有变体必须在同一批次中导入"
"。为确保不遗漏任何产品，请将导入批次大小设置为大于要导入的产品数量。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/import.rst:255
msgid ":doc:`variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:5
msgid ""
"Product variants are used to give single products a variety of different "
"characteristics and options for customers to choose from, such as size, "
"style, or color, just to name a few."
msgstr ""
"产品变体用于为单个产品提供多种不同的特征和选项供客户选择，例如尺寸、样式或颜"
"色等。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:8
msgid ""
"Product variants can be managed via their individual product template, or by "
"navigating to either the :guilabel:`Product Variants` "
"or :guilabel:`Attributes` page. All of these options are located within the "
"Odoo *Sales* application."
msgstr ""
"产品变体可以通过各自的产品模板进行管理，也可以导航到\\ :guilabel:`产品变体`\\"
" 或\\ :guilabel:`属性`\\ 页面进行管理。所有这些选项都位于 Odoo *销售*\\ 应用"
"程序中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:13
msgid ""
"An apparel company has the following variant breakdown for one of its best-"
"selling t-shirts:"
msgstr "一家服装公司的一款最畅销 T 恤的变体细分如下："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:15
msgid "Unisex Classic Tee"
msgstr "中性经典T恤"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:17
msgid "Color: Blue, Red, White, Black"
msgstr "颜色：蓝色、红色、白色、黑色"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:18
msgid "Size: S, M, L, XL, XXL"
msgstr "尺寸 : S, M, L, XL, XXL"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:20
msgid ""
"Here, the **T-shirt** is the product template, and **T-shirt: Blue, S** is a "
"specific product variant."
msgstr "在这里，**T恤**是产品模板，而**T恤：蓝色，S**是特定的产品变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Color** and **Size** are *attributes*, and the corresponding options (like "
"**Blue** and **S**) are *values*."
msgstr "**颜色**和**尺寸**是*属性*，相应的选项（如**蓝色**和**S**）是*值*。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:26
msgid ""
"In this instance, there is a total of twenty different product variants: "
"four **Color** options multiplied by five **Size** options. Each variant has "
"its own inventory count, sales totals, and other similar records in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"在这种情况下，总共有20个不同的产品变体：四个**颜色**选项乘以五个**尺寸**选项"
"。每个变体在Odoo中都有自己的库存计数、销售总额和其他类似记录。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`Product variants in the eCommerce <ecommerce/categories_variants/"
"product-variants>`"
msgstr ":ref:`电子商务中的产品变体 <ecommerce/categories_variants/product-variants>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:36
msgid ""
"To use product variants, go to :menuselection:`Sales --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, then enable the :guilabel:`Variants` feature in "
"the :guilabel:`Product Catalog` section, and click :guilabel:`Save` at the "
"top of the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""
"要使用产品变体,请转到\\ :menuselection:`销售 --> 配置 --> 设置`\\ ,然后在\\ "
":guilabel:`产品目录`\\ 部分中启用\\ :guilabel:`变体`\\ 功能,并点击\\ "
":guilabel:`设置`\\ 页面顶部的\\ :guilabel:`保存`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:43
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "属性"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:45
msgid ""
"Before product variants can be set up, attributes **must** be created. To "
"create, manage, and modify attributes, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Configuration --> Attributes`."
msgstr ""
"在设置产品变体之前，\\ **必须**\\ 先创建属性。要创建、管理和修改属性，请导航"
"至\\ :menuselection:`销售应用 --> 配置 --> 属性`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:49
msgid ""
"The order of attributes on the :guilabel:`Attributes` page dictates how they "
"appear on the *Product Configurator*, *Point of Sale* dashboard, and "
"*eCommerce* pages."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`属性`\\ 页面上的属性顺序决定了它们在\\ *产品配置器*、*POS*\\ 仪表"
"板和\\ *电子商务*\\ 页面上的显示方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:52
msgid ""
"To create a new attribute from the :guilabel:`Attributes` page, "
"click :guilabel:`New`. Doing so reveals a blank attributes form that can be "
"customized and configured in a number of ways."
msgstr ""
"要从\\ :guilabel:`属性`\\ 页面创建新属性，请点击\\ :guilabel:`新建`。这样会显"
"示一个空白的属性表单，可以通过多种方式进行自定义和配置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "A blank attribute creation form in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Odoo 销售应用中的空白属性创建表单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:58
msgid "First, create an :guilabel:`Attribute Name`, such as `Color` or `Size`."
msgstr "首先，创建一个\\ :guilabel:`属性名称`，例如 `颜色` 或 `尺寸`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:60
msgid ""
"Next, select one of the options from the :guilabel:`Display Type` field. "
"The :guilabel:`Display Type` determines how this product is shown on the "
"online store, *Point of Sale* dashboard, and *Product Configurator*."
msgstr ""
"接下来，从\\ :guilabel:`显示类型`\\ 字段中选择一个选项。:guilabel:`显示类"
"型`\\ 决定了该产品在在线商店、*POS*\\ 仪表板和\\ *产品配置器*\\ 上的显示方式"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:64
msgid "The following :guilabel:`Display Type` options are available:"
msgstr "以下\\ :guilabel:`显示类型`\\ 选项可用:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:68
msgid "Pills"
msgstr "Pills"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:70
msgid "Options appear as selectable buttons."
msgstr "选项显示为可选择的按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Pills display type"
msgstr "药丸显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:75
msgid "Color"
msgstr "颜色"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:77
msgid ""
"Options appear as small, colored circles; the colors can be defined using "
"any HTML color code."
msgstr "选项显示为小的彩色圆圈；颜色可以使用任何 HTML 颜色代码定义。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Color display type"
msgstr "颜色显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:82
msgid "Radio"
msgstr "单选"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:84
msgid "Options appear as radio buttons."
msgstr "选项显示为单选按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Radio display type"
msgstr "单选显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:89
msgid "Select"
msgstr "选择"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:91
msgid "Options appear in a drop-down menu."
msgstr "选项显示在下拉菜单中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Select display type"
msgstr "选择显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:96
msgid "Image"
msgstr "图片"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:98
msgid "Options appear as images."
msgstr "选项显示为图像。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Image display type"
msgstr "图片显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:103
msgid "Multi-checkbox"
msgstr "多选复选框"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:105
msgid ""
"Options appear as selectable checkboxes. This allows customers to choose "
"multiple options, e.g., to add extras to food orders or highly customizable "
"products."
msgstr ""
"选项显示为可选择的复选框。这允许客户选择多个选项，例如，向食品订单或高度可定"
"制的产品添加附加项。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:0
msgid "Multi-checkbox display type"
msgstr "多选复选框显示类型"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:111
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Variant Creation` field determines if/when a new variant is "
"automatically created once an attribute is added to a product."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`变体创建`\\ 字段决定是否/何时在将属性添加到产品后自动创建新变体"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:115
msgid ""
"If the attribute's :guilabel:`Display Type` is :guilabel:`Multi-checkbox`, "
"you **must** set the :guilabel:`Variant Creation` field to :guilabel:`Never`."
msgstr ""
"如果属性的\\ :guilabel:`显示类型`\\ 是\\ :guilabel:`多选复选框`，您\\ **必"
"须**\\ 将\\ :guilabel:`变体创建`\\ 字段设置为\\ :guilabel:`从不`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Instantly`: Creates all possible variants as soon as attributes "
"and values are added to a product template."
msgstr ":guilabel:`立即`：一旦将属性和值添加到产品模板，即创建所有可能的变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Dynamically`: Creates variants **only** when corresponding "
"attributes and values are added to a sales order."
msgstr ":guilabel:`动态`：**仅**\\ 在将相应的属性和值添加到销售订单时创建变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Never`: Prevents the automatic creation of purchaseable variants "
"with this tag. Instead, this tag is treated as being informational. If more "
"than one value is assigned to an attribute with this tag, all values are "
"loaded when the product displays, since the creation of discrete variants is "
"prevented."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`从不`：防止自动创建带有此标签的可购买变体。相反，此标签被视为信息"
"性质。如果将多个值分配给带有此标签的属性，则在显示产品时会加载所有值，因为阻"
"止了离散变体的创建。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:128
msgid ""
"Once added to a product, an attribute's :guilabel:`Variants Creation` mode "
"cannot be edited."
msgstr "将属性添加到产品后，该属性的\\ :guilabel:`变体创建`\\ 模式无法编辑。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`eCommerce Filter Visibility` field determines whether or not "
"these attribute options are visible to the customer on the front-end, as "
"they shop on the online store."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`电子商务筛选器显示` 字段位会决定客户在网上商店购物时，是否可以在前"
"端看到这些属性选项。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visible`: the attribute values are visible to customers on the "
"front-end."
msgstr ":guilabel:`显示`：前端客户可看见属性值。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hidden`: the attribute values are hidden from customers on the "
"front-end."
msgstr ":guilabel:`隐藏`：属性值会隐藏，不会向前端客户显示。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:136
msgid ""
"Lastly, in the optional :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` field, select a "
"category from a drop-down menu to group similar attributes under the same "
"section for added specificity and organization."
msgstr ""
"最后，在可选填的 :guilabel:`电子商务类别` 字段，从下拉式选单中选择一个类别，"
"将相似的属性分组至同一部份下，更方便整理及作个别设定。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:140
msgid ""
"To view the details related to the attribute category selected, click the "
"internal link :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(right arrow)` icon to the "
"far-right of the :guilabel:`eCommerce Category` field, once an option has "
"been selected. Doing so reveals that attribute category's detail form."
msgstr ""
"若要查看所选属性类别的详细资料，请在选取选项后，在 :guilabel:`电子商务类别` "
"栏位最右侧，点击内部连结 :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(右箭头)` 图示。这"
"样做会显示该属性类别的详细资料表单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"A standard attribute category detail page accessible via its internal link "
"arrow icon."
msgstr "可透过“内部连结”箭头图示存取的标准属性类别详细资讯页面。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:148
msgid ""
"Here, the :guilabel:`Category Name` and :guilabel:`Sequence` are displayed "
"at the top. Followed by :guilabel:`Related Attributes` associated with the "
"category. These attributes can be dragged and dropped into a desired "
"priority order."
msgstr ""
"此处顶部显示\\ :guilabel:`类别名称`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`序列`。下面显示与类别关"
"联的\\ :guilabel:`相关属性`。这些属性可以拖放到所需的优先级顺序。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:152
msgid ""
"Attributes can be directly added to the category, as well, by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr "您也可以点击 :guilabel:`新增资料行`，将属性直接新增至类别。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:155
msgid ""
"To create an attribute category directly from this field, start typing the "
"name of the new category, then select either :guilabel:`Create` "
"or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"若要直接在此字段内建立属性类别，您可开始输入新类别的名称，然后从显示的下拉式"
"功能表中，选择 :guilabel:`创建` 或 :guilabel:`创建并编辑⋯`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:159
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create` creates the category, which can be modified "
"later. Clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the category and "
"reveals a :guilabel:`Create Category` pop-up window, in which the new "
"attribute category can be configured and customized."
msgstr ""
"点击 :guilabel:`创建` 即可建立类别，稍后可以进行修改。点击 :guilabel:`创建并"
"编辑⋯` 会创建类别，并即时显示 :guilabel:`建立类别` 弹出视窗，该处可配置及自订"
"新的属性类别。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:164
msgid "Attribute values"
msgstr "属性值"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:166
msgid ""
"Attribute values should be added to the :guilabel:`Attribute Values` tab. "
"Values can be added to an attribute at any time, if needed."
msgstr ""
"属性值应加入至 :guilabel:`属性值` 分页中。如有需要，可以随时将属性值新增至属"
"性中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:169
msgid ""
"To add a value, click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Attribute "
"Values` tab."
msgstr "要加入新的值，请在 :guilabel:`属性值` 分页中，点击 :guilabel:`新增资料行`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:171
msgid ""
"Then, enter the name of the value in the :guilabel:`Value` column. Next, "
"check the box in the :guilabel:`Is custom value` column if the value is "
"custom (i.e., the customer gets to provide unique specifications that are "
"specific to this particular value)."
msgstr ""
"然后，在\\ :guilabel:`值`\\ 列中输入值的名称。接下来，如果该值是自定义的（即"
"客户可以提供特定于此特定值的独特规格），请选中\\ :guilabel:`是自定义值`\\ 列"
"中的复选框。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:176
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "颜色"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:178
msgid ""
"Next to :guilabel:`Display Type`, select the :guilabel:`Color` option. Go to "
"the :guilabel:`Attribute Values` tab to modify the value settings."
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`显示类型` 旁边，选择 :guilabel:`颜色` 选项。转到 :guilabel:`属"
"性值` 选项卡修改值设置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "Add an image of the pattern to an attribute."
msgstr "为属性添加图案图像。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:184
msgid ""
"To choose a color, click the blank circle in the :guilabel:`Color` column, "
"which reveals an HTML color selector pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"要选择颜色，请选择 :guilabel:`颜色` 列中的空白圆圈，系统会显示 HTML 颜色选择"
"器弹出视窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"Selecting a color from the HTML color pop-up window that appears on "
"attribute form."
msgstr "在属性表单上显示的 HTML 颜色弹出视窗中选择颜色。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:190
msgid ""
"In this pop-up window, select a specific color by dragging the color slider "
"to a particular hue and clicking on the color portion directly on the color "
"gradient window."
msgstr ""
"在此弹出窗口中，通过将颜色滑块拖动到特定色调并直接在颜色渐变窗口上单击颜色部"
"分来选择特定颜色。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:193
msgid ""
"Or, choose a specific color by clicking the *dropper* icon and selecting a "
"desired color that's currently clickable on the screen."
msgstr "或者，点击\\ *滴管*\\ 图标并选择屏幕上当前可点击的所需颜色来选择特定颜色。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:196
msgid ""
"If you sell products with specific patterns, you can also add an image to "
"display the pattern of the product. To do so, click the :icon:`fa-"
"camera` :guilabel:`(camera)` icon, then click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon and select an image from your local drive. "
"This pattern will appear as a color option on the eCommerce product page."
msgstr ""
"如果您销售具有特定图案的产品，您还可以添加图像来显示产品的图案。为此，点击\\ "
":icon:`fa-camera`:guilabel:`相机`\\ 图标，然后点击\\ :icon:`fa-"
"pencil`:guilabel:`铅笔`\\ 图标并从本地驱动器中选择图像。此图案将作为颜色选项"
"显示在电子商务产品页面上。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "Pattern as color option."
msgstr "图案作为颜色选项。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:205
msgid ""
"Attributes can also be created directly from the product template by adding "
"a new line and typing the name into the :guilabel:`Variants` tab."
msgstr "也可以直接在产品模板创建属性：添加行，在：guilabel：`变体`选项卡中输入名称。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:208
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is added to a product, that product is listed and "
"accessible via the attribute's :guilabel:`Related Products` smart button. "
"That button lists every product in the database currently using that "
"attribute."
msgstr ""
"将属性添加到产品后，该产品将通过属性的\\ :guilabel:`相关产品`\\ 智能按钮列出"
"并可访问。该按钮列出数据库中当前使用该属性的每个产品。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:215
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is created, use the attribute (and its values) to create a "
"product variant. To do that, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --"
"> Products`, and select an existing product to view that desired product's "
"form. Or, click :guilabel:`Create` to create a new product, to which a "
"product variant can be added."
msgstr ""
"创建属性后，使用该属性（及其值）创建产品变体。为此，请转到\\ "
":menuselection:`销售应用 --> 产品 --> 产品`，选择现有产品以查看所需产品的表单"
"。或者，点击\\ :guilabel:`创建`\\ 以创建新产品，然后可以为其添加产品变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:220
msgid ""
"On the product form, click the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab to "
"view, manage, and modify attributes and values for the product."
msgstr ""
"在产品表单上，点击\\ :guilabel:`属性与变体`\\ 选项卡以查看、管理和修改产品的"
"属性和值。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "The attributes and values tab on a typical product form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售中典型产品表单上的属性和值选项卡。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:226
msgid ""
"To add an attribute to a product and subsequent attribute values, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab. "
"Then, choose the desired attribute from the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"要向产品添加属性及后续属性值，请在\\ :guilabel:`属性与变体`\\ 选项卡中点击\\ "
":guilabel:`添加一行`。然后，从出现的下拉菜单中选择所需的属性。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:231
msgid ""
"Attributes can be created directly from the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& "
"Variants` tab of a product form. To do that, start typing the name of the "
"new attribute in the blank field, and select either :guilabel:`Create` "
"or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from the mini drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"可以直接从产品表单的\\ :guilabel:`属性与变体`\\ 选项卡创建属性。为此，在空白"
"字段中开始输入新属性的名称，然后从出现的迷你下拉菜单中选择\\ :guilabel:`创"
"建`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`创建并编辑...`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:236
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Create` creates the attribute, which can be customized "
"later. Clicking :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the attribute, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Attribute` pop-up form appears. In the pop-up form, "
"proceed to modify the attribute in a number of ways."
msgstr ""
"点击\\ :guilabel:`创建`\\ 会创建属性，稍后可以进行自定义。点击\\ "
":guilabel:`创建并编辑...`\\ 会创建属性，并出现一个\\ :guilabel:`创建属性`\\ "
"弹出表单。在弹出表单中，可以通过多种方式修改属性。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:240
msgid ""
"Once an attribute is selected in the :guilabel:`Attribute` column, proceed "
"to select the specific attribute values to apply to the product, via the "
"drop-down menu available in the :guilabel:`Values` column."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`属性`\\ 列中选择属性后，通过\\ :guilabel:`值`\\ 列中的下拉菜"
"单选择要应用于产品的特定属性值。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:245
msgid "There is no limit to how many values can be added."
msgstr "可以添加的值数量没有限制。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:248
msgid ""
"Similar product variant creation processes are accessible through the "
"Purchase, Inventory, and eCommerce applications."
msgstr "类似产品变体创建过程可在采购、库存和电子商务应用程序中完成。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:254
msgid "Configure variants"
msgstr "配置款式变体"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:256
msgid ""
"To the far-right of the attribute line is a :guilabel:`Configure` button. "
"When clicked, Odoo reveals a separate page showcasing those "
"specific :guilabel:`Product Variant Values`."
msgstr ""
"属性资料行的最右侧是 :guilabel:`配置` 按钮。按下时，Odoo 会显示一个独立页面，"
"展示这些特定的 :guilabel:`产品变体值`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Product Variant Values page accessible via the Configure button on a "
"product form."
msgstr "您可通过产品表单上的“配置”按钮，访问“产品变体值”页面。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:262
msgid ""
"Here, the specific :guilabel:`Value` name, :guilabel:`HTML Color Index` (if "
"applicable), and :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` are viewable."
msgstr ""
"在此处，可查看具体的 :guilabel:`性` 名称、:guilabel:`HTML 颜色代码`（如适用）"
"及 :guilabel:`属性值额外价格`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:266
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` represents the increase in the sales price "
"if the attribute is selected."
msgstr ":guilabel:`属性值额外价格` 表示如果选择该属性，销售价格会增加多少。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:269
msgid ""
"When a value is clicked on the :guilabel:`Product Variant Values` page, Odoo "
"reveals a separate page, detailing that value's related details."
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`产品变体值` 页面上按下某个值时，Odoo 会显示一个独立的页面，详细"
"说明该值的相关资料。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"A Product Variant Values page accessible via the Product Variants Values "
"general page."
msgstr "可通过“产品变体值”总览页面访问“产品变体值”详情页面。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:275
msgid ""
"On the specific product variant detail page, the :guilabel:`Value` "
"and :guilabel:`Value Price Extra` fields can be found, along with "
"an :guilabel:`Exclude for` field."
msgstr ""
"在具体的产品变体详情页面上，您可以看到 :guilabel:`值` 和 :guilabel:`额外价"
"格`字段，以及一个 :guilabel:`排除项`字段。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:278
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Exclude for` field, different :guilabel:`Product "
"Templates` and specific :guilabel:`Attribute Values` can be added. When "
"added, this specific attribute value will be excluded from those specific "
"products."
msgstr ""
"在 :guilabel:`排除项`字段中，可以添加不同的 :guilabel:`产品模板`和特定的 "
":guilabel:`属性值`。添加后，此特定属性值将从那些指定的产品中排除。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:285
msgid "Variants smart button"
msgstr "变体智能按钮"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:287
msgid ""
"When a product has attributes and variants configured in "
"its :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab, a :guilabel:`Variants` smart "
"button appears at the top of the product form. The :guilabel:`Variants` "
"smart button indicates how many variants are currently configured for that "
"specific product."
msgstr ""
"当一个产品在其 :guilabel:`属性与变体`标签页中配置了属性和变体后，产品表单的顶"
"部就会出现一个 :guilabel:`变体`智能按钮。该:guilabel:`变体`智能按钮会显示当前"
"为该特定产品配置的变体数量。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid "The variants smart button at the top of the product form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售应用中，产品表单顶部的“变体”智能按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:294
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Variants` smart button is clicked, Odoo reveals a "
"separate page showcasing all the specific product variant combinations "
"configured for that specific product."
msgstr ""
"点击 :guilabel:`变体`智能按钮后，Odoo 会打开一个单独的页面，显示为该特定产品"
"配置的所有具体的产品变体组合。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The variants page accessible via the variants smart button on the product "
"form in Odoo."
msgstr "在 Odoo 中，通过产品表单上的“变体”智能按钮可访问的变体页面。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:301
msgid "Impact of variants"
msgstr "变体的影响"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:303
msgid ""
"In addition to offering more detailed product options to customers, product "
"variants have their own impacts that can be taken advantage of throughout "
"the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"除了为客户提供更详细的产品选项外，产品变体在 Odoo 数据库中还有其自身的影响力"
"，可以加以利用。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:306
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Barcode`: barcodes are associated with each variant, instead of "
"the product template. Each individual variant can have its own unique "
"barcode/SKU."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`条形码`：条形码与每个变体关联，而不是与产品模板关联。每个独立的变"
"体都可以有自己独特的条形码/SKU（库存单位）。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:308
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Price`: every product variant has its own public price, which is "
"the sum of the product template price *and* any extra charges for particular "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`价格`：每个产品变体都有其自己的公开价格，该价格是产品模板价格与特"
"定属性额外费用的总和。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:312
msgid ""
"A red shirt's sales price is $23 -- because the shirt's template price is "
"$20, plus an additional $3 for the red color variant. Pricelist rules can be "
"configured to apply to the product template or to the variant."
msgstr ""
"红色衬衫的销售价格为 23 美元——因为衬衫的模板价格为 20 美元，加上红色变体额外"
"的 3 美元。价格表规则可以配置为应用于产品模板或变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:316
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inventory`: Inventory is counted for each individual product "
"variant. On the product template form, the inventory reflects the sum of all "
"variants, but the actual inventory is computed by individual variants."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`库存`：库存按每个单独的产品变体计数。在产品模板表单上，库存反映所"
"有变体的总和，但实际库存是按单个变体计算的。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:321
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manufacturing`: a single BoM can be used for multiple variants of "
"the same product."
msgstr ":guilabel:`制造`\\ ：单个物料清单可用于同一产品的多个变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:320
msgid ""
"Refer to :doc:`../../../../inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/"
"advanced_configuration/product_variants` documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"有关更多信息，请参阅\\ :doc:`../../../../inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/"
"advanced_configuration/product_variants`\\ 文档。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:323
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Picture`: each product variant can have its own specific picture."
msgstr ":guilabel：`图片`：每个产品变体都可以有特定图片。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:326
msgid ""
"Changes to the product template automatically apply to every variant of that "
"product."
msgstr "对产品模板的更改将自动应用于产品的所有变体。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:329
msgid "Adding and deleting attributes from product variants"
msgstr "在产品变体中添加和删除属性"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:331
msgid ""
"When attributes are added or deleted from products, variants that have "
"already been created are affected. Depending on whether or not these "
"variants have been used in orders, they are archived or deleted and "
"recreated."
msgstr ""
"当在产品中添加或删除属性时，已创建的变体会受到影响。根据这些变体是否已在订单"
"中使用，它们将被归档或删除并重新创建。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:335
msgid ""
"Variants that have not been used in an order are deleted and recreated with "
"the new attributes. This may result in the deletion of additional "
"customizations, depending on how the variants were configured."
msgstr ""
"未在订单中使用过的变体将被删除并使用新属性重新创建。这可能导致删除其他自定义"
"设置，具体取决于变体的配置方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:338
msgid ""
"Variants that have been previously used in one or more orders are archived "
"and removed from the product catalog instead of being deleted."
msgstr ""
"之前已在一个或多个订单中使用过的变体将被归档并从产品目录中移除，而不是被删除"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:342
msgid ""
"A business offers leather motorcycle jackets with the following attributes "
"and values for a total of 27 product variants:"
msgstr "一家企业提供皮革摩托车夹克，具有以下属性和值，共计 27 个产品变体："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:345
msgid "Size: Small, Medium, Large"
msgstr "尺寸：小、中、大"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:346
msgid "Color: Black, Brown, Natural"
msgstr "颜色：黑色、棕色、原色"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:347
msgid "Material: Leather, Vegan Leather, Premium Leather"
msgstr "材质：皮革、纯素皮革、高级皮革"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:349
msgid ""
"Due to rising costs, the business makes the decision to stop offering "
"different leathers and removes the \"Material\" attribute from the product "
"form. This has the following effects:"
msgstr ""
"由于成本上涨，该企业决定停止提供不同的皮革，并从产品表单中移除\"材质\"属性。"
"这将产生以下影响："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:352
msgid "Any leather jacket variants that have been sold will be archived"
msgstr "任何已售出的皮夹克变体将被归档"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:353
msgid "Any leather jacket variants that have not been sold will be deleted"
msgstr "任何未售出的皮夹克变体将被删除"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:354
msgid ""
"A new set of variants using just Size and Color attributes will be created, "
"for a total of 9 product variants"
msgstr "将仅使用尺寸和颜色属性创建一组新变体，共计 9 个产品变体"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:357
msgid ""
"The business owner can find archived product variants by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Product Variants`, clicking "
"the drop-down in the search bar, and finally clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Archived filter`. Any deleted variants and their "
"customizations will be lost."
msgstr ""
"企业所有者可以通过导航至\\ :menuselection:`销售应用 --> 产品 --> 产品变体`\\ "
"，点击搜索栏中的下拉菜单，最后点击\\ :guilabel:`已归档筛选器`\\ 来查找已归档"
"的产品变体。任何已删除的变体及其自定义设置都将丢失。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/variants.rst:363
msgid ":doc:`import`"
msgstr ":doc:`import`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:3
msgid "Returns and refunds"
msgstr "退货和退款"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app provides two different ways to process returns. The "
"method used depends on whether or not an invoice has been sent."
msgstr ""
"Odoo\\ *销售*\\ 应用提供两种不同的方式来处理退货。使用的方法取决于是否已发送"
"发票。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:11
msgid "Before invoicing"
msgstr "开票前"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:13
msgid ""
"Returns are completed using *Reverse Transfers* when a customer decides to "
"return a product **before** an invoice has been sent or validated."
msgstr ""
"当客户决定在发票发送或验证\\ **之前**\\ 退货时，使用\\ *反向调拨*\\ 完成退货"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:17
msgid ""
"In order to use *Reverse Transfers*, the *Inventory* app **must** be "
"installed."
msgstr "要使用\\ *反向调拨*，\\ **必须**\\ 安装\\ *库存*\\ 应用。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:19
msgid ""
"To start a return before invoicing, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales` "
"app, select the desired sales order, and click on the :guilabel:`Delivery` "
"smart button to open the associated delivery order."
msgstr ""
"要在开票前开始退货，请导航至\\ :menuselection:`销售`\\ 应用，选择所需的销售订"
"单，然后点击\\ :guilabel:`交付`\\ 智能按钮以打开相关的交付订单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A typical sales order with a highlighted delivery smart button in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo\\ :guilabel:`销售`\\ 中典型的销售订单，其中突出显示了交付智能按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:27
msgid "On the validated delivery order, click :guilabel:`Return`."
msgstr "在已确认的交付订单上，点击\\ :guilabel:`退货`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A validated delivery order with a highlighted Return button in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo\\ :guilabel:`销售`\\ 中已确认的交付订单，其中突出显示了退货按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:33
msgid "This opens a :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr "这将打开\\ :guilabel:`反向调拨`\\ 弹出窗口。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:35
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Quantity` matches the validated quantities from "
"the delivery order. Update the quantities, if necessary. Click on "
"the :guilabel:`🗑️ (trash)` icon next to a line item to remove it from the "
"return."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，\\ :guilabel:`数量`\\ 与交付订单中的已确认数量相匹配。如有必要，"
"请更新数量。点击行项目旁边的\\ :guilabel:`🗑️（垃圾桶）`\\ 图标可将其从退货中"
"移除。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"The \"Reverse Transfer\" pop-up window, to make a return before invoicing "
"the customer."
msgstr "\"反向调拨\"弹出窗口，用于在向客户开票之前进行退货。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:43
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Return` to confirm the return. This generates a new "
"warehouse operation for the incoming returned product(s)."
msgstr ""
"接下来，点击\\ :guilabel:`退货`\\ 以确认退货。这将为退回的产品生成新的仓库操"
"作。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Warehouse operation after a return has been confirmed in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "在Odoo\\ :guilabel:`销售`\\ 中确认退货后的仓库操作。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:50
msgid ""
"Upon receiving the return, the warehouse team validates the warehouse "
"operation by clicking :guilabel:`Validate`. Then, on the original sales "
"order, the :guilabel:`Delivered` quantity updates to reflect the difference "
"between the initial validated quantities and the returned quantities."
msgstr ""
"收到退货后，仓库团队通过点击\\ :guilabel:`确认`\\ 来确认仓库操作。然后，在原"
"始销售订单上，\\ :guilabel:`已交付`\\ 数量会更新，以反映初始已确认数量与退货"
"数量之间的差异。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"The updated \"Delivered\" quantity on the sales order after the reverse "
"transfer."
msgstr "反向调拨后销售订单上更新的\"已交付\"数量。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:58
msgid ""
"When an invoice is created, the customer receives an invoice **only** for "
"the products they are keeping, if any."
msgstr "创建发票时，客户仅会收到保留产品（如有）的发票。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:64
msgid "After invoicing"
msgstr "开票后"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:66
msgid ""
"Sometimes, customers return an item after they receive and/or pay for their "
"invoice. In these cases, a return using only *Reverse Transfers* is "
"insufficient since validated, or sent, invoices cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"有时，客户会在收到和/或支付发票后退货。在这种情况下，仅使用*反向调拨*是不够的"
"，因为已确认或已发送的发票无法更改。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:70
msgid ""
"However, *Reverse Transfers* can be used in conjunction with *Credit Notes* "
"to complete the customer's return."
msgstr "但是，*反向调拨*可以与*信用凭证*结合使用，以完成客户的退货。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:73
msgid ""
"To start a return after invoicing, navigate to the relevant sales order in "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr "要在开票后开始退货，请导航至\\ :menuselection:`销售`\\ 应用中的相关销售订单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:76
msgid ""
"If there is a payment registered on the sales order, the payment details "
"appear in the chatter, and the invoice (accessible through "
"the :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button) has a green :guilabel:`In Payment` "
"banner."
msgstr ""
"如果销售订单上记录了付款，付款详细信息会显示在聊天记录中，并且发票（可通过\\ "
":guilabel:`发票`\\ 智能按钮访问）会显示绿色的\\ :guilabel:`付款中`\\ 横幅。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Sample of a green in payment banner in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo\\ :guilabel:`销售`\\ 中绿色付款中横幅的示例。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:84
msgid ""
"From the sales order, click on the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button to view "
"the validated delivery order. Then, click :guilabel:`Return` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Reverse Transfer` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"在销售订单中，点击 :guilabel:`送货` 智能按钮，查看已验证的送货订单。然后，点"
"击 :guilabel:`退货` 弹出 :guilabel:`逆向转移` 窗口。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:87
msgid ""
"Next, edit the :guilabel:`Product` and/or :guilabel:`Quantity`, as needed "
"for the return. Then, click :guilabel:`Return`. This generates a new "
"warehouse operation for the incoming returned product(s), which is validated "
"by the warehouse team once the return is received by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"然后，根据退货的需要编辑 :guilabel:`产品` 和/或 :guilabel:`数量`。然后，点击 "
":guilabel:`退货`。这将为收到的退货产品生成一个新的仓库操作，一旦收到退货，点"
"击 :guilabel:`验证` 即可由仓库团队进行验证。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:92
msgid ""
"Then, on the sales order, the :guilabel:`Delivered` quantity updates to "
"reflect the difference between the initial validated quantities and the "
"returned quantities."
msgstr ""
"然后，在销售订单上，更新 :guilabel:`已送达` 数量，以反映初始验证数量和退回数"
"量之间的差额。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:95
msgid ""
"To process a refund, navigate to the relevant invoice (from the sales order, "
"click on the :guilabel:`Invoices` smart button). Then, click "
"the :guilabel:`Credit Note` button at the top of the validated invoice."
msgstr ""
"要处理退款，请导航至相关发票（从销售订单点击 :guilabel:`发票` 智能按钮）。然"
"后，点击已验证发票顶部的 :guilabel:`贷记单` 按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid ""
"A typical customer invoice with a Credit Note button highlighted in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售系统中的常规客户发票，突出显示贷记单按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:103
msgid "Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Credit Note` pop-up form."
msgstr "这样做会弹出 :guilabel:`贷记单` 表单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:None
msgid "Typical credit note pop-up form that appears in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售系统中出现的常规贷记单弹出窗口。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:109
msgid ""
"Start by entering a :guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note` and a "
"specific :guilabel:`Journal` to process the credit. Then, select a "
"specific :guilabel:`Reversal Date`."
msgstr ""
"首先输入 :guilabel:`贷记单上显示的原因` 和特定的 :guilabel:`日记账` 来处理贷"
"记。然后，选择特定的 :guilabel:`逆转日期`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:112
msgid ""
"After the information is filled in, click :guilabel:`Reverse` "
"or :guilabel:`Reverse and Create Invoice`. Then, edit the draft, if needed."
msgstr ""
"填写信息后，点击 :guilabel:`逆转` 或 :guilabel:`逆转和创建发票`。然后，根据需"
"要编辑草稿。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:115
msgid "Lastly, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the credit note."
msgstr "最后，点击 :guilabel:`确认`，以确认贷记单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:117
msgid ""
"When complete, a blue banner reading: :guilabel:`You have outstanding "
"credits for this customer. You can allocate them to mark this invoice as "
"paid.` appears at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"完成后，页面顶部会出现一个蓝色横幅： :guilabel:`您有该客户的未结贷项。您可直"
"接抵扣，以将此发票标记为已付清。`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/returns.rst:121
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"
