#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:213
msgid ""
"When creating a PDF, it's best practice to use common dynamic form fields "
"(:guilabel:`user_id_name`, :guilabel:`partner_id_name`, "
"and :guilabel:`name`). When uploaded into the database, Odoo auto-populates "
"those fields with the information from their respective fields."
msgstr ""
"创建 PDF 时，最佳做法是使用常见动态表单栏位"
"（:guilabel:`user_id_name`、:guilabel:`partner_id_name`\\ 和\\ "
":guilabel:`name`）。上传到数据库后，Odoo 会自动使用各栏位中的信息填充这些栏位"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:217
msgid ""
"In this case, Odoo would auto-populate the Salesperson's name in "
"the :guilabel:`user_id_name` dynamic text field, the Sales Order Reference "
"in the :guilabel:`name` field, and the Customer Name in "
"the :guilabel:`partner_id_name` field."
msgstr ""
"在这种情况下，Odoo 会在\\ :guilabel:`user_id_name`\\ 动态文本栏位中自动填充销"
"售人员姓名，在\\ :guilabel:`name`\\ 栏位中填充销售订单参考，在\\ "
":guilabel:`partner_id_name`\\ 栏位中填充客户名称。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:0
msgid "PDF quote being built using common dynamic placeholders."
msgstr "使用常用动态占位符创建 PDF 报价单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:5
msgid ""
"Reusable quotation templates can be made in Odoo's **Sales** app for common "
"products or services."
msgstr "可以在Odoo的\\ **销售**\\ 应用中为常见产品或服务创建可重用的报价模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:7
msgid ""
"By using these templates, quotations can be tailored and sent to customers "
"at a quicker pace, without having to create new quotations from scratch "
"every time a sales negotiation occurs."
msgstr ""
"通过使用这些模板，可以更快地定制报价并发送给客户，而无需在每次销售谈判时从头"
"开始创建新报价。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:13
msgid ""
"To use quotation templates, begin by activating the setting "
"in :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Quotations &_Orders` heading."
msgstr ""
"要使用报价模板，首先在\\ :menuselection:`销售应用 --> 配置 --> 设置`\\ 中激活"
"该设置，然后滚动到\\ :guilabel:`报价与订单`\\ 标题。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:16
msgid ""
"Under the heading, tick the :guilabel:`Quotation Templates` checkbox. Doing "
"so reveals a new :guilabel:`Default Template` field, in which a default "
"quotation template can be chosen from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"在该标题下，勾选\\ :guilabel:`报价模板`\\ 复选框。这样做会显示一个新的\\ "
":guilabel:`默认模板`\\ 字段，可以从下拉菜单中选择默认报价模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid "How to enable quotation templates on Odoo Sales."
msgstr "如何在Odoo销售中启用报价模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:23
msgid ""
"Upon activating the :guilabel:`Quotation Template` feature, an "
"internal :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Quotation Templates` link appears "
"beneath the :guilabel:`Default Template` field."
msgstr ""
"激活\\ :guilabel:`报价模板`\\ 功能后，:icon:`fa-arrow-right`\\ :guilabel:`报"
"价模板`\\ 内部链接会出现在\\ :guilabel:`默认模板`\\ 字段下方。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:26
msgid ""
"Clicking this link reveals the :guilabel:`Quotation Templates` page, from "
"which templates can be created, viewed, and edited."
msgstr ""
"点击此链接会显示\\ :guilabel:`报价模板`\\ 页面，可以从中创建、查看和编辑模板"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:29
msgid ""
"Before leaving the :guilabel:`Settings` page, do not forget to click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button to save all changes made during the session."
msgstr ""
"在离开\\ :guilabel:`设置`\\ 页面之前，不要忘记点击\\ :guilabel:`保存`\\ 按钮"
"以保存会话期间所做的所有更改。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:35
msgid "Create quotation templates"
msgstr "创建报价模板"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:37
msgid ""
"To create a quotation template, click the :guilabel:`Quotation Templates` "
"link on the :guilabel:`Settings` page once :guilabel:`Quotation templates` "
"are enabled, or navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> "
"Quotation Templates`. Both options reveal the :guilabel:`Quotation "
"Templates` page, where quotation templates can be created, viewed, and "
"edited."
msgstr ""
"要创建报价单模板，在启用\\ :guilabel:`报价单模板`\\ 后，点击\\ :guilabel:`设"
"置`\\ 页面上的\\ :guilabel:`报价单模板`\\ 链接，或导航至\\ :menuselection:`销"
"售应用 --> 配置 --> 报价单模板`\\ 。这两个选项都会显示\\ :guilabel:`报价单模"
"板`\\ 页面，在此可以创建、查看和编辑报价单模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid "Quotation templates page in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Odoo销售应用中的报价单模板页面。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:45
msgid ""
"To create a new quotation template, click the :guilabel:`New` button, "
"located in the upper-left corner. Doing so reveals a blank quotation "
"template form that can be customized."
msgstr ""
"要创建新报价单模板，请点击位于左上角的\\ :guilabel:`新建`\\ 按钮。这将显示一"
"个可自定义的空白报价单模板表单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid "Create a new quotation template on Odoo Sales."
msgstr "在Odoo销售上创建新报价单模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:51
msgid ""
"Start by entering a name for the template in the :guilabel:`Quotation "
"Template` field."
msgstr "首先在\\ :guilabel:`报价单模板`\\ 字段中输入模板名称。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:53
msgid ""
"Then, in the :guilabel:`Quotation Validity` field, designate how many days "
"the quotation template will remain valid for, or leave the field on the "
"default `0` to keep the template valid indefinitely."
msgstr ""
"然后，在\\ :guilabel:`报价单有效期`\\ 字段中，指定报价单模板的有效天数，或将"
"该字段保留为默认值`0`以使模板永久有效。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:57
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Confirmation Mail` field, click the blank drop-down "
"menu to select a preconfigured email template to be sent to customers upon "
"confirmation of an order."
msgstr ""
"接下来，在\\ :guilabel:`确认邮件`\\ 字段中，点击空白下拉菜单以选择预配置的电"
"子邮件模板，该模板将在订单确认时发送给客户。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:61
msgid ""
"To create a new email template directly from the :guilabel:`Confirmation "
"Mail` field, start typing the name of the new email template in the field, "
"and select either: :guilabel:`Create` or :guilabel:`Create and edit...` from "
"the drop-down menu that appears."
msgstr ""
"要直接从\\ :guilabel:`确认邮件`\\ 字段创建新电子邮件模板，请在该字段中开始输"
"入新电子邮件模板的名称，然后从出现的下拉菜单中选择：:guilabel:`创建`\\ 或\\ "
":guilabel:`创建并编辑...`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:65
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Create` creates the email template, which can be edited "
"later."
msgstr "选择\\ :guilabel:`创建`\\ 将创建电子邮件模板，稍后可以进行编辑。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:67
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Create and edit...` creates the email template, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Confirmation Mail` pop-up window appears, in which the "
"email template can be customized and configured immediately."
msgstr ""
"选择\\ :guilabel:`创建并编辑...`\\ 将创建电子邮件模板，并显示\\ :guilabel:`创"
"建确认邮件`\\ 弹出窗口，可以立即自定义和配置电子邮件模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid ""
"Create confirmation mail pop-up window from the quotation template form in "
"Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo销售报价单模板表单中的创建确认邮件弹出窗口。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:74
msgid ""
"When all modifications are complete, click :guilabel:`Save & Close` to save "
"the email template and return to the quotation form."
msgstr ""
"完成所有修改后，点击\\ :guilabel:`保存并关闭`\\ 以保存电子邮件模板并返回报价"
"单表单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:77
msgid ""
"If working in a multi-company environment, use the :guilabel:`Company` field "
"to designate to which company this quotation template applies."
msgstr ""
"如果在多公司环境中工作，请使用\\ :guilabel:`公司`\\ 字段指定此报价单模板适用"
"于哪个公司。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:80
msgid ""
"If a journal is set in the :guilabel:`Invoicing Journal` field, all sales "
"orders with this template will invoice in that specified journal. If no "
"journal is set in this field, the sales journal with the lowest sequence is "
"used."
msgstr ""
"如果在\\ :guilabel:`开票日记账`\\ 字段中设置了日记账，则使用此模板的所有销售"
"订单都将在该指定日记账中开票。如果此字段中未设置日记账，则使用序列号最低的销"
"售日记账。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:84
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Online Signature` and/or :guilabel:`Online Payment` "
"features are activated in the :guilabel:`Settings` (:menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Configuration --> Settings`), those options are available on "
"quotation template forms."
msgstr ""
"如果在\\ :guilabel:`设置`\\ （:menuselection:`销售应用 --> 配置 --> 设置`\\ "
"）中启用了\\ :guilabel:`在线签名`\\ 和/或\\ :guilabel:`在线付款`\\ 功能，这些"
"选项将在报价单模板表单中可用。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:88
msgid ""
"Check the box beside :guilabel:`Online Signature` to request an online "
"signature from the customer to confirm an order."
msgstr "勾选\\ :guilabel:`在线签名`\\ 旁边的复选框以要求客户提供在线签名来确认订单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:91
msgid ""
"Check the box beside :guilabel:`Online Payment` to request an online payment "
"from the customer to confirm an order. When :guilabel:`Online Payment` is "
"checked, a new percentage field appears, in which a specific percentage of "
"payment can be entered."
msgstr ""
"勾选\\ :guilabel:`在线付款`\\ 旁边的复选框以要求客户提供在线付款来确认订单。"
"勾选\\ :guilabel:`在线付款`\\ 后，将出现一个新的百分比字段，可以在其中输入具"
"体的付款百分比。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:95
msgid ""
"Both options, :guilabel:`Online Signature` and :guilabel:`Online Payment` "
"can be enabled simultaneously, in which case the customer must provide "
"**both** a signature **and** a payment to confirm an order."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`在线签名`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`在线付款`\\ 两个选项可以同时启用，在这"
"种情况下，客户必须**同时**提供签名**和**付款才能确认订单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:100
msgid "Lines tab"
msgstr "明细行标签页"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:102
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Lines` tab, products can be added to the quotation "
"template by clicking :guilabel:`Add a product`, organized by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add a section` (and dragging/dropping section headers), "
"and further explained with discretionary information (such as warranty "
"details, terms, etc.) by clicking :guilabel:`Add a note`."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`明细行`\\ 标签页中，可以通过点击\\ :guilabel:`添加产品`\\ 将"
"产品添加到报价单模板，通过点击\\ :guilabel:`添加部分`\\ （并拖放部分标题）进"
"行组织，以及通过点击\\ :guilabel:`添加备注`\\ 使用自定义信息（如保修详情、条"
"款等）进一步说明。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:107
msgid ""
"To add a product to a quotation template, click :guilabel:`Add a product` in "
"the :guilabel:`Lines` tab of a quotation template form. Doing so reveals a "
"blank field in the :guilabel:`Product` column."
msgstr ""
"要向报价模板添加产品，请在报价模板表单的\\ :guilabel:`行`\\ 标签页中点击\\ "
":guilabel:`添加产品`。这样做会在\\ :guilabel:`产品`\\ 列中显示一个空白字段。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:110
msgid ""
"When clicked, a drop-down menu with existing products in the database "
"appears. Select the desired product from the drop-down menu to add it to the "
"quotation template."
msgstr ""
"点击后，会出现一个包含数据库中现有产品的下拉菜单。从下拉菜单中选择所需产品，"
"将其添加到报价模板中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:113
msgid ""
"If the desired product is not readily visible, type the name of the desired "
"product in the :guilabel:`Product` field, and the option appears in the drop-"
"down menu. Products can also be found by clicking :guilabel:`Search More...` "
"from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"如果所需产品未直接显示，请在\\ :guilabel:`产品`\\ 字段中输入所需产品的名称，"
"该选项将出现在下拉菜单中。也可以通过点击下拉菜单中的\\ :guilabel:`搜索更"
"多...`\\ 来查找产品。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:118
msgid ""
"It is possible to add event-related products (booths and registrations) to "
"quotation templates. To do so, click the :guilabel:`Product` field, type in "
"`Event`, and select the desired event-related product from the resulting "
"drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"可以将活动相关产品（展位和注册）添加到报价模板中。为此，请点击\\ "
":guilabel:`产品`\\ 字段，输入\"活动\"，然后从结果下拉菜单中选择所需的活动相关"
"产品。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:123
msgid ""
"When a product is added to a quotation template, the "
"default :guilabel:`Quantity` is `1`, but that can be edited at any time."
msgstr "将产品添加到报价模板时，默认\\ :guilabel:`数量`\\ 为1，但可以随时编辑。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:126
msgid ""
"Then, drag and drop the product to the desired position, via "
"the :guilabel:`six squares` icon, located to the left of each line item."
msgstr ""
"然后，通过位于每个行项目左侧的\\ :guilabel:`六个方格`\\ 图标，将产品拖放到所"
"需位置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:129
msgid ""
"To add a *section*, which serves as a header to organize the lines of a "
"sales order, click :guilabel:`Add a section` in the :guilabel:`Lines` tab. "
"When clicked, a blank field appears, in which the desired name of the "
"section can be typed. When the name has been entered, click away to secure "
"the section name."
msgstr ""
"要添加*章节*（用作组织销售订单行的标题），请在\\ :guilabel:`行`\\ 标签页中点"
"击\\ :guilabel:`添加章节`。点击后，会出现一个空白字段，可在其中输入所需的章节"
"名称。输入名称后，点击其他位置以确定章节名称。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:134
msgid ""
"Then, drag and drop the section name to the desired position, via "
"the :icon:`oi-apps` :guilabel:`(six squares)` icon, located to the left of "
"each line item."
msgstr ""
"然后，通过位于每个行项目左侧的\\ :icon:`oi-apps`\\ :guilabel:`（六个方格）`\\"
" 图标，将章节名称拖放到所需位置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:137
msgid ""
"To add a note, which appears as a piece of text for the customer on the "
"quotation, click :guilabel:`Add a note` in the :guilabel:`Lines` tab. When "
"clicked, a blank field appears, in which the desired note can be typed. When "
"the note has been entered, click away to secure the note."
msgstr ""
"要添加备注（在报价单上显示为客户的一段文字），请在\\ :guilabel:`行`\\ 标签页"
"中点击\\ :guilabel:`添加备注`。点击后，会出现一个空白字段，可在其中输入所需的"
"备注。输入备注后，点击其他位置以确定备注。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:141
msgid ""
"Then, drag and drop the note to the desired position, via the :icon:`oi-"
"apps` :guilabel:`(six squares)` icon."
msgstr ""
"然后，通过\\ :icon:`oi-apps`\\ :guilabel:`（六个方格）`\\ 图标，将备注拖放到"
"所需位置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:144
msgid ""
"To delete any line item from the :guilabel:`Lines` tab (product, section, "
"and/or note), click the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(remove record)` icon on "
"the far-right side of the line."
msgstr ""
"要从\\ :guilabel:`行`\\ 标签页中删除任何行项目（产品、章节和/或备注），请点击"
"行右侧的\\ :icon:`fa-trash`\\ :guilabel:`（删除记录）`\\ 图标。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:150
msgid ""
"Using *optional products* is a marketing strategy that involves the cross-"
"selling of products along with a core product. The aim is to offer useful "
"and related products to customers, which may result in an increased sale."
msgstr ""
"使用*可选产品*是一种营销策略，涉及在核心产品的基础上交叉销售产品。目的是为客"
"户提供有用的相关产品，这可能会增加销售额。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:155
msgid ""
"If a customer wants to buy a car, they have the choice to order massaging "
"seats as an additional product that compliments the car, or ignore the offer "
"and buy the car alone."
msgstr ""
"如果客户想购买汽车，他们可以选择订购按摩座椅作为补充汽车的附加产品，或者忽略"
"该优惠仅购买汽车。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:158
msgid ""
"Optional products appear as a section on the bottom of sales orders and "
"eCommerce pages. Customers can immediately add them to their online sales "
"orders themselves, if desired."
msgstr ""
"可选产品显示为销售订单和电子商务页面底部的一个章节。客户可以根据需要立即将其"
"添加到在线销售订单中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid "Optional products appearing on a typical sales order with Odoo Sales."
msgstr "选购产品在 Odoo 销售应用程式的典型销售订单上显示。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:164
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab, :guilabel:`Add a line` for each "
"cross-selling product related to the original items in the :guilabel:`Lines` "
"tab, if applicable."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`可选产品`\\ 标签页中，如适用，为与\\ :guilabel:`行`\\ 标签页"
"中原始项目相关的每个交叉销售产品\\ :guilabel:`添加一行`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:167
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Add a line` reveals a blank field in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` column."
msgstr ":guilabel:`加入数据行` 后，系统会在 :guilabel:`产品` 列显示一个空白字段。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:169
msgid ""
"When clicked, a drop-down menu with products from the database appear. "
"Select the desired product from the drop-down menu to add it as an optional "
"product to the quotation template."
msgstr ""
"点击后，会出现一个包含数据库中产品的下拉菜单。从下拉菜单中选择所需的产品，将"
"其作为可选产品添加到报价模板中。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:172
msgid ""
"To delete any line item from the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab, click "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(remove record)` icon."
msgstr ""
"要删除 :guilabel:`可选产品` 标签页中的任何行项目，请点击 :icon:`fa-"
"trash`:guilabel:`（删除记录）`图标。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:176
msgid "Optional products are **not** required to create a quotation template."
msgstr "**并非必须** 要有可选购产品，才可创建报价单模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:179
msgid "Terms & Conditions tab"
msgstr "条款和条件标签页"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:181
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Terms & Conditions` tab provides the opportunity to add terms "
"and conditions to the quotation template. To add terms and conditions, type "
"the desired terms and conditions in this tab."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`条款和条件`选项卡提供了向报价模板添加条款和条件的机会。要添加条款"
"和条件，请在此选项卡中键入所需的条款和条件。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:185
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:188
msgid ""
"Terms and conditions are **not** required to create a quotation template."
msgstr "**并非必须** 要有条款及条件细则，才可建立报价单模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:191
msgid "Use quotation templates"
msgstr "使用报价单模板"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:193
msgid ""
"When creating a quotation (:menuselection:`Sales app --> New`), choose a "
"preconfigured template in the :guilabel:`Quotation Template` field."
msgstr ""
"创建报价单时（:menuselection:`销售应用程序 --> 新建`），在 :guilabel:`报价单"
"模板`字段中选择一个预配置模板。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:197
msgid ""
"The order of the templates in the :guilabel:`Quotation Template` field is "
"determined by the order of the templates in the Quotation Templates form. "
"The order of the quotations in the Quotation Templates form does **not** "
"affect anything else."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`报价模板`\\ 字段中模板的顺序由报价模板表单中模板的顺序决定。报价模"
"板表单中报价的顺序**不会**影响其他任何内容。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:201
msgid ""
"To view what the customer will see, click the :guilabel:`Preview` button at "
"the top of the page to see how the quotation template appears on the front-"
"end of the website through Odoo's customer portal."
msgstr ""
"若要查看客户将看到的内容，请点击页面顶部的 :guilabel:`预览` 按钮，透过 Odoo "
"的客户门户网站，查看报价模板在网站前端将会如何显示。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid "Customer preview of a quotation template in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Odoo 销售应用程序中，报价单模板的客户预览。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:208
msgid ""
"When all blocks and customizations are complete, click the :guilabel:`Save` "
"button to save the configuration."
msgstr "完成所有区块和自定义设置后，点击 :guilabel:`保存` 按钮保存配置。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:211
msgid ""
"The blue banner located at the top of the quotation template preview can be "
"used to quickly return :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Back to edit mode`. "
"When clicked, Odoo returns to the quotation form in the back-end of the "
"*Sales* application."
msgstr ""
"报价单模板预览顶部的蓝色横幅可用于快速返回 :icon:`fa-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`返回编辑模式`。点击后，Odoo 将返回 *销售* 应用程序后端的报价单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:216
msgid "Mass cancel quotations/sales orders"
msgstr "批量取消报价单/销售订单"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:218
msgid ""
"Cancel multiple quotations (or sales orders) by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations` dashboard, landing, "
"by default, in the list view. Then, on the left side of the table, tick the "
"checkboxes for the quotations to be canceled."
msgstr ""
"通过导航至 :menuselection:`销售应用程序 --> 订单 --> 报价单` 仪表板，取消多个"
"报价单（或销售订单），默认情况下，该仪表板位于列表视图中。然后，在表格左侧勾"
"选要取消的报价单复选框。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:223
msgid ""
"Select all records in the table by selecting the checkbox column header at "
"the top-left of the table; the total number of selected items are displayed "
"at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"通过选择表格左上方的复选框列标题，选择表格中的所有记录；页面顶部会显示所选项"
"目的总数。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, with the desired quotations (or sales orders) selected from the list "
"view on the :guilabel:`Quotations` page, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button to reveal a drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"然后，从 :guilabel:`报价单` 页面的列表视图中选择所需的报价单（或销售订单），"
"点击 :icon:`fa-cog`:guilabel:`操作`按钮，显示一个下拉菜单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:230
msgid "From this drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`Cancel quotations`."
msgstr "从下拉菜单中选择 :guilabel:`取消报价`。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Cancel quotations option on the Actions drop-down menu in the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr "Odoo 销售应用程序操作下拉菜单上的取消报价单选项。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:236
msgid ""
"This action can be performed for quotations in *any* stage, even if it is "
"confirmed as a sales order."
msgstr "此操作可以在*任何*阶段对报价单执行，即使已确认为销售订单。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:239
msgid ""
"Upon selecting the :guilabel:`Cancel quotations` option, a :guilabel:`Cancel "
"quotations` confirmation pop-up window appears. To complete the "
"cancellation, click the :guilabel:`Cancel quotations` button."
msgstr ""
"选择\\ :guilabel:`取消报价单`\\ 选项后，会出现一个\\ :guilabel:`取消报价单`\\"
" 确认弹出窗口。要完成取消，请点击\\ :guilabel:`取消报价单`\\ 按钮。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:244
msgid ""
"An error pop-up message appears when attempting to cancel an order for an "
"ongoing subscription that has an invoice."
msgstr "尝试取消具有发票的正在进行的订阅的订单时，会出现错误弹出消息。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:5
msgid "Shopee Connector"
msgstr "Shopee 连接器"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:7
msgid ""
"The **Shopee Connector** synchronizes orders between Shopee and Odoo, which "
"considerably reduces the amount of time spent manually entering Shopee "
"orders (from the Shopee Seller account) into Odoo. It also allows users to "
"accurately keep track of Shopee sales in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Shopee 连接器**\\ 可同步 Shopee 与 Odoo 之间的订单，大幅减少手动将 Shopee "
"订单（来自 Shopee 卖家账户）输入 Odoo 所花费的时间。它还允许用户在 Odoo 中准"
"确跟踪 Shopee 销售情况。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:14
msgid "The **Shopee Connector** is able to:"
msgstr "**Shopee 连接器**\\ 能够："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:16
msgid ""
"Synchronize (Shopee to Odoo) all confirmed orders, and their order items, "
"which include:"
msgstr "同步（从 Shopee 到 Odoo）所有已确认订单及其订单项目，包括："

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:22
msgid ""
"Synchronize (Odoo to Shopee) all available quantities of your products "
"(:abbr:`FBM (Fulfilled by Merchant)`)."
msgstr "同步（从 Odoo 到 Shopee）您产品的所有可用数量（:abbr:`FBM（商家自配送）`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:25
msgid "Support multiple Shopee marketplaces (shops) per seller account."
msgstr "支持每个卖家账户的多个 Shopee 市场（店铺）。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/shopee_connector.rst:28
msgid ""
"The **Shopee Connector** is designed to synchronize sales orders data. Other "
"actions, such as downloading weekly/monthly income/fees reports, handling "
"disputes, or issuing refunds, **must** be managed from the *Shopee Seller "
"Central*, as usual."
msgstr ""
"**Shopee 连接器**\\ 旨在同步销售订单数据。其他操作，例如下载每周/每月收入/费"
"用报告、处理纠纷或发起退款，\\ **必须**\\ 照常在\\ *Shopee 卖家中心*\\ 中进行"
"管理。"

